!.env.example
# Non-secret build flag: forces the prod game-client URLs (game/beta.heroesofcrypto.io) instead of
# the localhost dev fallbacks in the play/sandbox launcher pages. Committed so `bun run build`
# (CI + manual deploys) always produces a production-correct static site.
!.env.production

